quran[5{c,v,t}:
4,7,"mardon ke liye uss maal mein hissa hai jo maa baap aur rishta daaron ne chorra ho, aur aurton ke liye bhi uss maal mein hissa hai jo maa baap aur rishta daaron ne chorra ho, khuwa thora ho ya bohat, aur yeh hissa ( Allah ki taraf se ) muqarrar hai"
4,8,aur jab taqseem ke mauqa par kunba ke log aur yateem aur maskeen ayen to is maal mein se un ko bhi kuch do aur unn ke sath bhallay manson ki si baat karo
4,9,logon ko is baat ka khayaal kar ke darna chahiye ke agar woh khud apne peechay be bas aulaad chortay to martay waqt inhen apne bachon ke haq mein kaisay kuch andaishay la-haq hotay pas chahiye ke woh khuda ka khauf karen aur raasti ki baat karen
4,10,jo log zulm ke sath yatimon ke maal khatay hain Dur haqeeqat woh apne pait aag se bhartay hain aur woh zaroor jahannum ki bharakti hui aag mein jhonkay jayen ge
4,11,"tumhari aulaad ke baray mein Allah tumhe hadaayat karta hai ke : mard ka hissa do aurton ke barabar hai, agar ( maiyat ki waris ) do se zayed larkiyan hon to inhen trke ka do tahai diya jaye, aur agar aik hi larki waris ho to aadha tarka is ka hai agar maiyat sahib aulaad ho twas ke walidain mein se har aik ko trke ka chhata hissa milna chahiye aur agar woh sahib aulaad nah ho aur walidain hi is ke waris ho n to maa ko teesra hissa diya jaye aur agar maiyat ke bhai behan bhi hon to maa chhatay hissa ki haq daar hogi ( yeh sab hissay uss waqt nikalay jayen ) jabkay wasiyat jo maiyat ne ki ho poori kar di jaye aur qarz jo uss par ho ada kar diya jaye tum nahi jantay ke tumahray maa baap aur tumhari aulaad mein se kon bilhaaz naffa tum se qareeb tar hai yeh hissay Allah ne muqarrar kar diye hain, aur Allah yaqeenan sab haqeeqaton se waaqif aur saari maslehton ka jan-nay wala hai"
